# 4-tier ramp 요약
@tier_table
  | Tier  | Source                       | Throughput   | Cost          | Lead-time | Access         |
  |-------|------------------------------|--------------|---------------|-----------|----------------|
  | T1    | ANU length=1024              | 8192 bit/sec | free          | 즉시      | public-api     |
  | T2    | IBM Quantum vacuum           | 100 bit/sec  | free-tier     | 1-2주     | auth-api       |
  | T3    | ID Quantique Quantis IDQ     | 4 Mbit/sec   | $1k-10k paid  | 4-8주     | commercial-hw  |
  | T4    | KAIST quantum-optical        | 1 Gbit/sec   | free/sponsored| 1-3개월   | research-only  |

@strategic_note 4-tier 는 cost-vs-throughput-vs-lead-time 의 Pareto frontier — 동시 진행하면 7주 내 4 source 모두 가용.
@strategic_note T1 (ANU 1024) 는 1-line patch + queue management 만 필요해 단일 cycle 에 가능. T2-T4 는 외부 의존.

# Tier-1 (ANU length=1024 — 즉시)
@t1_blocker state/blockers/qrng_anu_length_1024_patch.hexa
@t1_target tool/noise_envelope.hexa:165
@t1_change `length=1` → `length=1024` + 1024-byte queue management (in-memory or state/kick/cache/anu_byte_queue/)
@t1_compat KICK_BETA_HW_SOURCE env opt-in (default urandom 미회귀, raw 47 backward-compat)
@t1_selftest 6/6 미회귀 검증 + KICK_BETA_REAL_ANU=1 success path 신규 fixture
@t1_throughput_target ≥ 1024 bit per request × 1 req/sec budget held over N=10 cycles
@t1_falsifier 1 req → < 1024 byte returned (ANU API param 무시 OR rate-limit 변경) = ANU side spec drift, retire OR adapt
@t1_eta 2026-04-27 ~ 2026-04-29 (1-3 days)

# Tier-2 (IBM Quantum vacuum — 1-2주)
@t2_blocker state/blockers/qrng_ibm_quantum_integration.hexa
@t2_prereq_chain
  step 1: IBM Quantum 가입 — https://quantum-computing.ibm.com/ (이메일 + 학술/연구 정보)
  step 2: API token 생성 — IBM Cloud → IAM → API keys → Create
  step 3: token 보관 — ~/.qiskit/qiskit-ibm.json (chmod 600) 또는 IBM_QUANTUM_TOKEN env (.env / shell rc)
  step 4: Python qiskit + qiskit-ibm-runtime install — `pip install qiskit qiskit-ibm-runtime` (Python venv 권장)
  step 5: hexa wrapper — tool/qrng_ibm_bridge.hexa (exec subprocess Python script: import qiskit_ibm_runtime → vacuum_fluctuation_circuit → execute → parse byte → emit JSON)
  step 6: tool/noise_envelope.hexa β-channel KICK_BETA_HW_SOURCE=ibm 분기 + fallback to urandom on auth-fail
  step 7: selftest fixture KICK_BETA_HW_SOURCE=ibm + mock token
@t2_throughput_target 100 bit/sec (free-tier, IBM Q open-plan rate-limit)
@t2_falsifier IBM Q free-tier 변경 → throughput < 50 bit/sec OR auth 절차 추가 = adapt OR retire
@t2_paid_upgrade IBM Quantum Premium ($1k+/month) → throughput up + queue priority

# Tier-3 (ID Quantique Quantis IDQ — 4-8주, paid)
@t3_blocker state/blockers/qrng_quantis_idq_procurement.hexa
@t3_prereq_chain
  step 1: 모델 선택 — Quantis USB-200 (~$1-2k, 200 kbit/sec) / Quantis-PCIe-40M (~$5-10k, 40 Mbit/sec) / Quantis Appliance 2.0 (~$10k+, multi-rack)
  step 2: vendor procurement — https://www.idquantique.com/contact/ (IDQ Korea agent 또는 직접 sales 협의)
  step 3: Korea import shipping — 통관 + DHL/FedEx 항공 ~2-4주
  step 4: driver install — Linux idQ kernel module (Mac 호환성 vendor 확인 필요; Mac 미지원 시 Linux host (ubu1/ubu2/htz) 에 mount)
  step 5: physical mount — USB-200 = host USB port / PCIe-40M = host PCIe slot (ubu1 unused slot 확인 필요) / Appliance = rack mount + Ethernet
  step 6: C library binding — `libquantis.so` 또는 raw device read `/dev/qrandom0` (Linux) — hexa exec subprocess C tool wrapper
  step 7: tool/qrng_quantis_bridge.hexa (exec around vendor CLI 또는 raw device cat) + tool/noise_envelope.hexa KICK_BETA_HW_SOURCE=quantis 분기
@t3_throughput_target ≥ 4 Mbit/sec (PCIe-40M @ rated 40 Mbit/sec; USB-200 @ ~200 kbit/sec)
@t3_falsifier hardware DOA OR driver Mac/Linux 호환성 fail = vendor return OR Linux host fallback
@t3_cost_estimate USD 1000-10000 (모델별); shipping + customs ~10% 추가; 보증 1-3년 vendor

# Tier-4 (KAIST quantum-optical research-collab — 1-3개월)
@t4_blocker state/blockers/qrng_kaist_collaboration.hexa
@t4_prereq_chain
  step 1: KAIST PI 식별 — KAIST 물리학과 + 전자공학과 quantum optics group 연락처 조사 (kaist.ac.kr 학과 directory + Google Scholar quantum optics KAIST 저자)
  step 2: collaboration proposal draft — 본 nexus project 의 noise envelope / kick distinguishability + entropy multiplexer 의 학술 가치 명시 + research-grade entropy source 가 필요한 이유 + 협력 형태 (data-sharing / co-author)
  step 3: collaboration agreement 체결 — KAIST IRB-equivalent + nexus 측 data-handling 정책 + 학술 발표 권리 분배
  step 4: technical onboarding — KAIST device API protocol / data format / network setup spec 수령
  step 5: access setup — VPN-tunneled or direct-network 또는 physical visit (방문) — KAIST 측 설정 의존
  step 6: tool/qrng_kaist_bridge.hexa — KAIST protocol around hexa exec subprocess
  step 7: tool/noise_envelope.hexa KICK_BETA_HW_SOURCE=kaist + IRB ethics clearance for publication
@t4_throughput_target 1 Gbit/sec (KAIST experimental setup rated)
@t4_falsifier collaboration agreement 거절 OR 학술 절차 6개월 초과 = retire OR alternative research-lab approach
@t4_alt 다른 research lab — Seoul National University / POSTECH / Pohang Light Source / 한국과학기술원 (KIST) 양자광학 그룹

# 병렬 ramp 일정
@ramp_schedule
  Week 0 (today, 2026-04-27): T1 (ANU 1024 patch) start + T2 (IBM 가입) initiate + T3 (vendor 조사) initiate + T4 (KAIST PI 조사) initiate
  Week 1: T1 commit + selftest PASS / T2 token + Python install / T3 vendor quote + 모델 결정 / T4 PI 첫 연락
  Week 2: T2 hexa wrapper draft / T3 purchase order / T4 proposal draft
  Week 3-4: T2 selftest + integration / T3 shipping + driver / T4 agreement 진행
  Week 5-6: T3 mount + binding / T4 onboarding
  Week 7-8: T3 hexa wrapper + integration / T4 access setup
  Week 9-12: T4 wrapper + IRB

